^\[DEBUG\] Destroying daemons$
^\[INFO\] Ceph configfile on host ceph001 may be removed$
^\[INFO\] Commands to be run manually:$
^\[INFO\] su - ceph -c /usr/bin/ceph-deploy --cluster ceph mds destroy ceph001.cubone.os$
^\[INFO\] su - ceph -c /usr/bin/ceph-deploy --cluster ceph osd destroy osd.0$
^\[DEBUG\] restarting daemons$
^\[INFO\] Commands to be run manually:$
^\[INFO\] su - ceph -c ceph001 /sbin/service ceph restart mon$
^\[INFO\] su - ceph -c ceph001 /sbin/service ceph stop osd.1$
^\[INFO\] su - ceph -c ceph002 /sbin/service ceph start mds$
